<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Video Processing Complete</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: #10b981;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-top: none;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #10b981;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .video-info {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Video Processing Complete!</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Great news! Your video "{{videoTitle}}" has been successfully processed and is ready to publish.</p>
    <div class="video-info">
      <h3>Video Details:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}}</li>
        <li><strong>Resolution:</strong> {{resolution}}</li>
        <li><strong>Formats:</strong> {{formats}}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p>You can now publish your video to your connected social media accounts.</p>
    <a href="{{videoUrl}}" class="button">View Video</a>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The NEXUS Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
